  <!-- EN: deadlife pack -->
  <Apparel_DeadlifePack.label>死灵背包</Apparel_DeadlifePack.label>
  <!-- EN: A single-use pack that launches a capsule which explodes into deadlife dust. The dust animates human and animal corpses as shamblers that will only attack your enemies.\n\nDeadlife dust is composed of microscopic machine-like archites which hang in the air. The archites are similar to those in archotech resurrector serums, but are overpowered and chaotic. Where they touch a corpse, they induce a chaotic and violent resurrection. -->
  <Apparel_DeadlifePack.description>一次性背包，可发射一枚胶囊，胶囊爆炸后会释放出死灵烟尘。这种烟尘会将人类以及动物的尸体变成只会攻击敌人的蹒跚怪。\n\n死灵烟尘由漂浮在空气中的纳米微械构成。这些纳米微械与超凡科技复活液中的那些类似，但死灵烟尘中的纳米微械更加强效，更加混乱。它们一旦接触到尸体，便会引发混乱而剧烈的复生行为。</Apparel_DeadlifePack.description>
  <!-- EN: charge -->
  <Apparel_DeadlifePack.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>充能</Apparel_DeadlifePack.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: deploy deadlife dust -->
  <Apparel_DeadlifePack.verbs.deploy_deadlife_dust.label>释放死灵烟尘</Apparel_DeadlifePack.verbs.deploy_deadlife_dust.label>
  
  <!-- EN: disruptor flare pack -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.label>干扰照明弹背包</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.label>
  <!-- EN: A utility pack that shoots disruptor flares. On impact, the flare burns a capsule of bioferrite, which creates a bright flash and a local psychic disruption. This stuns psychically sensitive creatures, revealing those that are invisible, and reducing their consciousness and movement speed for a short while. Afterwards, the flare continues to burn, lighting up a wide area for some time. -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.description>发射干扰照明弹的通用背包。照明弹命中后，其内含的灵铁便会剧烈燃烧，产生耀眼的闪光并施加小范围的灵能干扰。能够暂时眩晕灵能敏感生物，并使隐形生物无所遁形，还能在短时间内降低它们的意识以及移动速度。之后照明弹会继续燃烧，在一段时间内照亮大片区域。</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.description>
  <!-- EN: charge -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>充能</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: deploy flare -->
  <Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.verbs.deploy_flare.label>部署照明弹</Apparel_DisruptorFlarePack.verbs.deploy_flare.label>
  
  <!-- EN: turret pack -->
  <Apparel_PackTurret.label>炮塔背包</Apparel_PackTurret.label>
  <!-- EN: A wearable pack that allows the user to deploy a battery-powered turret. The pack contains a propulsion device, letting the user launch the turret a short distance. These turrets are effective for flanking and distracting enemies. However, the turret's limited AI can't be directly controlled, so it can cause friendly fire incidents. The turret battery lasts for several hours. -->
  <Apparel_PackTurret.description>可穿戴式背包，使用它可以部署一个电池供电的炮塔。背包中自带推进装置，可在短距离内将炮塔发射出去。这种炮塔可有效包抄敌人并分散其注意力。不过炮塔的AI能力有限，无法直接控制，因此可能造成友军误伤事件。炮塔的电池可持续使用数小时。</Apparel_PackTurret.description>
  <!-- EN: charge -->
  <Apparel_PackTurret.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>充能</Apparel_PackTurret.comps.CompApparelVerbOwner_Charged.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: deploy turret -->
  <Apparel_PackTurret.verbs.deploy_turret.label>部署炮塔</Apparel_PackTurret.verbs.deploy_turret.label>
  
